Package game

Class Config

java.lang.Object
game.Config
public class Config
extends java.lang.Object
Overview - Represents the game settings. Contains no logic, just holds values. UseCase - an instance will be passed to other methods or objects, which can pull info from it FYI - When instantiated, the initial fields are set to default values, which represent a basic easy game
